<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_530_r1l26"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Jacob vns <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> etlıch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> von <expan>Jr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>arme<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_530_r1l27">leẅt <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu wentelſtein fürbracht / wıe ein Jr <expan>recht<ex>er</ex></expan> gſchol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_530_r1l28">den Jn in ır kırchen ʒu wentelſtein geprochen vnd Jr hab dar </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_530_r1l29">awſʒ geſtolen hab ʒu eẅch gen <expan>alrſp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> ſey . <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_530_r1l30">etlıch ʒu eẅch <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeyn vnd rechts ʒu <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> kırchen = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_530_r1l31">prüchel ʒu <expan>helff<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>t</expan> vnd <expan>geford<ex>er</ex>t</expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> . daʒ Jn von </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_531" id="264v"/>
<ab facs="#facs_531_r2l1">eẅch nıht hab geen <expan>mug<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ vns fremd neͣme . Alſo <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_531_r2l2">wır ʒu eẅch <expan>hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> Erlpeken <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> . dem wır befolhen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_531_r2l3"><expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> mıt eẅch <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>red<ex>en</ex></expan> / vnd <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewch was <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_531_r2l4"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu dıſem mal von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> ın </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_531_r2l5"><expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> ſachen an eẅch <expan>w<ex>er</ex>be</expan> . daʒ Jr Jm das <expan>gencʒl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gelawbet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_531_r2l7">vnd eẅch 
<add><ab facs="#facs_531_r2l6">auch </ab></add> darinn beweıſet vnd tuet als ʒu <expan>ſöllıche<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ſache<ex>n</ex></expan> pıllıch </ab>
