<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Jacob, uns <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        etlich <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> von
                                <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>arme<ex>n</ex></expan> lewt <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> zu
                        Wentelstein fürbracht, wie ein ir <expan>recht<ex>er</ex></expan> gschol,
                        den in in ir kirchen zu Wentelstein geprochen und ir hab darawsz gestolen
                        hab, zu ewch gen <expan>Alrsp<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> sey, <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ir etlich
                        zu ewch <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> seyn und rechts zu
                                <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan> kirchenprüchel zu
                                <expan>helff<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>beg<ex>er</ex>t</expan> und <expan>geford<ex>er</ex>t</expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz in von <pb facs="#facs_531" id="264v"/>ewch niht
                        hab geen <expan>mug<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz uns fremd neͣme. Also
                                <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan> wir zu ewch
                            <expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> Erlpeken, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, dem wir befolhen
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, mit ewch <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> zu
                                <expan>red<ex>en</ex></expan>; und <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        ewch, was <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> zu disem mal von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und der <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> in <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan> sachen an
                        ewch <expan>w<ex>er</ex>be</expan>, daz ir im das
                            <expan>genczl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gelawbet und ewch <add>auch</add>
                        darinn beweiset und tuet, als zu <expan>sölliche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan> pillich gebürt und wir ewch getrawen. Das
                        wellen etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii<hi rend="sup">a</hi> xi<hi rend="sup">m</hi>
<expan>virginu<ex>m</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
